<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span> صحيح - <span class="c2">((الإرواء)</span>) <span class="c2">(٨/ ٢٩٣/٢٦٧٦)</span> , <span class="c2">((صحيح أبي داود)</span>) <span class="c2">(١٨٠٥)</span>: ق.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>